def crazyend() :
    print("'There is no one in the house', they try to explain as you yell something about the ‘intruder’ getting away. There is an intruder, you know it! Or is there? Do you know it? Did you see him? Did you even see what caused the noise? No, you panicked over nothing, didn’t you? You mutter to yourself, confused and erratic, you’re so deep in the spiral you don’t even protest as they help you into their car, and next thing you know...white walls, white shirt, a nice doctor giving you some white pills. Huh, the psych yard is not that bad.")
    print("You obtained the Crazy ending")

def bedroomcos() :
    choice = input("choose A[Hide in the closet] B[Jump out the window]")
    if choice == "A" :
        if StressLvl >= 3 :
            print("The stress of your decisions makes you feel uneasy and lightheaded. You clutch your chest as you feel a sharp pain. The world drifts outside your vision. You suffered from a heart attack.")
        else :
            print("With only seconds to spare, you hide in the closet. The thief runs into the room and your breath becomes constricted. The thief hears your loud breathing and opens the door. The intruder lounges at you. Despite your best attempt you’ve been got. How about you try again? ")
            generalbad()
    elif choice == "B" :
        if StressLvl >= 3 :
            print("The stress of your decisions makes you feel uneasy and lightheaded. You clutch your chest as you feel a sharp pain. The world drifts outside your vision. You suffered from a heart attack.")
        else :
            print("With only seconds to spare, you make the irrational decision to jump out of the window. The window is large, so you make it outside without any problems. You hesitate slightly on the ledge, but the loud footsteps snap you out of the daydream. You jump, landing unsuccessfully on your leg, but you feel none of it. Pure adrenaline forces you to continue to run away as the thief stays back baffled by the window. ")
            jumpoutwin()
    else :
        print("Oops invaild option.. Try again..")
        bedroomcos()
    
