            print("You grab your phone and pray you get lucky and the call will go through. It does, you dial 911 and an operator answers. ")
            print("It takes police almost an hour to get to you, by then you’ve almost driven yourself crazy, huddling in your bed behind locked doors. You hear the policemen knock, bolting downstairs and ripping the door open, meeting the two men with a panicked look. ")
            print("It takes them 10 minutes to sweep the cabin during which you wait at the front door. They come back, looking at your disheveled appearance and crazed eyes. ")
